Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,NETFLIX オリジナルシリーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）私は橘(たちばな)アイコ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Aiko Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に会えた　もう１人の私
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally met the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）はっ！\N（グミ）キュ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚かせてごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はあなたと話がしたかっただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ… 私と？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:36.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:39.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）ずっと待ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのことを知ってから ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I first found out about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中学の制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my junior high uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バースト前の私…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me from before the Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:50.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓(かえで)）\Nここも攻撃されて危ないってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this place get attacked, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹(かずき)）\Nシェルターなんてあるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes!\N-Then let's get there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石(しらいし)）ええ\N（楓）だったら すぐ行こうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉(ゆうや)）やめさせないと\N（一樹）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-We have to stop it!\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N外部攻撃では\Nマターは根絶できない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An external attack\Nwon't wipe out the Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:38.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ 本物の橘アイコの脳による\Nマターへの制御が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It will destroy\Nthe only thing holding the matter back--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全に失われることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko Tachibana's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香(はるか)）\N今まで以上の大活性を\N招くことになると？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it will make it more active?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we return the artificial brain\Nto the Matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:53.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\Nだが それも人工生体脳を\Nマター本体に返せば すべて終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it will end all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模(さがみ)）\Nなら俺は お前の望みどおりに\N動いてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）相模さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:01.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\Nそいつが 篠(しの)さんの残した道だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mission\NShino left for us to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）あっ くっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the key to this whole thing.\NWhat's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\Nそれなのに 要であるお前が\Nなぜ そんな顔をする？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:13.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが お前の\N成し遂げるべきことなんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided yourself\Nthat you must do this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:20.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バーストを終息させ\N橘アイコを元の体に戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end the Burst, and return\NAiko Tachibana to her real body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが俺の目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのために…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためだけに\N橘をここまで連れてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only reason\NI brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！\Nお前 本気で言ってんのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the time you've spent with her,\Ndon't you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけアイコちゃんと一緒にいて\Nお前は何も思わないのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして そこまで\N橘のことに干渉する？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so concerned about Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ 言わせるなよ　分かるだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it! You know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はアイコちゃんのことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）おかしいかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:54.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなも仲間だって\Nそう思ってたんじゃないのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were friends!\NHaven't you felt anything for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:00.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなのにアイコちゃんが\N偽物だっていうんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you say Aiko is artificial!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この気持ちは何だっていうんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So why am I having these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは事実を誤認した上での感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're feelings\Nbased on a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認識を改めれば済むことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Change your thinking and they'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ！ 偉い研究者かなんか\N知らないけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be some famous researcher,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけは俺にも分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but even I understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前みたいなヤツは 誰も…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も救うことなんかできない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,can never save anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）一樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 来る！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）もう隠す必要もない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hide it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N俺が橘を見つけます\N皆さんは 下へ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find Tachibana. You keep descending!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）おい 神崎(かんざき)！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）神崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）私と話したい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）だけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私って… 何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは… あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）神崎君 言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:56.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の私は 作り物なんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that the other me was artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消しちゃうんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That she'd be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いやることは必要ないって…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Her thoughts are no longer necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって 私のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But he meant me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）そんなことない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が 今 こうして\Nここにいられるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole existence, here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのおかげなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the same, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントは\Nあなたも思ってるんでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に早く消えてほしいって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get rid of me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ そんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じられないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 もう 何も信じられるものがない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe anything anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの日 起こったこと\Nそれからのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know what happened that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたに全部 知ってもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything that happened since,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys take the stairs down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\Nお前ら 施設内の階段で下へ行け
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はこっちを行く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）ちょっ 何 バカなこと！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go the same way,\Nthe activity will focus there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\N同じ道を行けば活性化が集中する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）だからって あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちも急ごう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）楓\N（楓）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kaede!\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）こっちは大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）なんで あいつなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't save Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつがアイコちゃんの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）\N活性源が さらに広がってるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The activity is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良(ゆら)君の研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Yura's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\Nえっ 由良博士の？ ここが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This is Dr. Yura's lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:43.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:49.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,白石さんは神崎が由良博士だと\Nご存じだったんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you knew that Kanzaki is Dr. Yura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\N博士は 橘さんの脳が人工生体だと\Nあなたにも言わなかったんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he tell you\Nthat Tachibana's brain was artificial?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は最初から\N私たち全員をだましていたんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's deceived all of us\Nfrom the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後まで だまされたまま\Nミッションが成功していれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If we completed the mission\Nwithout knowing the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:15.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちはアイコちゃんに対して\N何の呵責(かしゃく)もなくいられた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,none of us would have felt\Nany remorse or guilt toward Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイコちゃん自身も
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Aiko herself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しみを感じないまま\Nこの世から消え去ることができた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,would have left this world\Nwithout any mental anguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his way\Nof taking responsibility for his sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼なりの罪の背負い方だったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But he failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）でも 破綻した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）\Nそう　私たちは知ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We know all about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ その行く末を\N見届けなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so,\Nhe has to see this through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっとそう言うわ 大輔(だいすけ)なら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain Daisuke would feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:49.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人… 型…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Human form...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finally met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\N目が覚めると 私は独りだった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I woke up, I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:24.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコの思念）\Nたしか私 お父さんと事故に遭って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wasn't I in an accident with Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う？ 私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I wrong? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:33.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\N私は いつの間にか\N自分の体をなくしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I had lost my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? When? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコの思念）\Nなぜ？ いつ？ どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I dead? Is this heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は死んだの？ ここは あの世？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\N私は これまでの記憶を\N手繰りはじめたの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I started going back\Nthrough all my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコの思念）\Nこれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, I found myself overcome\Nwith memories I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\Nそして 本当なら\N私が知れるはずのない記憶が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:56.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あふれでてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコの思念）\N誰？ 私はどこにいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is this? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さん 亮太(りょうた)は…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are Mom and Ryota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\N何かよくないことが起きてるって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I understood that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけは私にも分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}something terrible was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコの思念）\Nあっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:45.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\Nそれから私は 独りで漂い続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, I found myself floating all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこへも行くことはできなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも\Nお母さんと亮太を守れたから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so,\NI was able to protect Mom and Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコの思念）\N大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:09:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:09:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だんだん 私は\N私が分からなくなっていった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,gradually I've been losing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\Nこのまま消えるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If it keeps up, I might disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:12.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ意識が遠くなって…\Nそんな感じがした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like my consciousness\Nis slowly slipping away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 悲しくも怖くもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I don't feel sad or afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）うっ　うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）あっ ここ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）ハァ ハァ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さみしかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to see you, Dr. Yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会いたかった 由良先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 柚葉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと待ってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待っていた？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You waited?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm begging you. Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　お願い 私を助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（由良）\Nこれは夢？\Nそれともドリームコンタクト？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this a dream? Or is it Dream Contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:03.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）\N先生 あのね 体が動かせないの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yura, I can't move my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:08.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,声も出せなくて\Nお父さんと話もできない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't speak! I can't even talk to Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 どうしたらいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（由良）\Nやはり意識を取り戻していたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must have regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人型マターは\N柚葉ちゃんが動かして…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human form Matter\Nis controlled by Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 独りぼっちは いや！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早くここから出たい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:26.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の体は…\N君は今 どんな様子なんだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your body now?\NWhat is its condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない\N私は どこに行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:35.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（由良）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと独りだったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been alone this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 私 見つけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I found something that helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の心を照らしてくれる光を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every day I saw your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were like a light\Nshining into my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:53.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,毎日 夢のように\N私は あなたの記憶を見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたから流れてくる\Nうれしい気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your happy memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しい気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}your sad memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんな気持ちが\N私を私でいさせてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and everything else flowed into me,\Nand kept me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたを通して 笑うことができた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through you, I was able to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒ったり泣いたりすることができた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was able to feel anger and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が今 こうして\Nここにいられるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのおかげ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）私の？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\Nここまで来てくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　え？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!\NI want you to rescue Mom and Ryota!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い\Nお母さんと亮太を助け出してほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:34.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\N伊佐津(いさづ)先生の話 私にも聞こえてた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what Dr. Isazu said, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻撃が始まる前に\N２人を連れて ここから逃げて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the attack starts,\Nget them and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）え？ 逃げるって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことしたら あなたは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間がないの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の時間も もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“私の時間”って…\Nあなたの意識のこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your time? Do you mean your consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（官房長官）\N政府は これを他国からの\N武力攻撃に準ずる事態と認定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The government recognizes this\Nas an armed attack by a foreign nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国民保護法に基づき\N陸海空自衛隊に対し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is an official announcement that\Nthe Malignant Area will be incinerated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:11.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マリグナント･エリア焼灼(しょうしゃく)作戦\N任務の開始を発令したことを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the land, air, and sea branches\Nof the Self-Defense Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国民の皆さんに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ノック）\N（伊佐津）どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竹原(たけはら)）先生 政府の発表ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the government has announced
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the attack will\Ncenter on Research Facility Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの第二研が\N攻撃の中心になるかと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\Nちょうどよかった 竹原君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing, Takehara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘アイコ君を迎えに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I must hurry to Primary Point\Nto get Aiko Tachibana,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急ぎ プライマリー･ポイントへ\N向かわねばならなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竹原）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マター化人工生体細胞の\N活性制御を行う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and suppress the artificial cells\Nthat have turned into Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,留守を頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take over in my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 先生 何の話を？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐保(さほ)）ごめんね 柚葉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柚葉）\N助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（由良）待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:55.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の体の様子を何でもいい\N分かることを教えてくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me anything you know about your body.\NAnything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からないの 何にも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know a single thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の体はどこにあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い 由良先生 助けて…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Dr. Yura! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）あっ！ 由良先生が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）ん？ どうかしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私がマターの体を押さえこんでみる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to suppress the Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少ししかできないかもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I might not be much use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:19.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:23.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは私にしかできないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:36.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しの時間だったけど\Nあなたと話せて うれしかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have much time,\Nbut I'm glad I got to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？ ちょっと待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 まだ\Nあなたに聞きたいことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have so much to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大臣）今更 何のつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原(なんばら)）\Nですから 自衛隊による作戦を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I'm requesting that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,即刻 中止するよう\Nお願いしているんです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the Self-Defense Forces' attack\Nstop immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:57.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の一存で覆すことなどできん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be stopped\Nbased on your opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよりも自分の身を\N案ずるべきではないのかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be more concerned\Nabout your own position,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nanbara of the Matter Control Agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マター対策統括の南原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀(ほり)）うひっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:10.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで この状況を容認してきた\N君の責任は重いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The responsibility for letting\Nthis situation continue is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:15.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,境界線地区に残ったダイバーの\N始末を早急に進めたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal with the remaining Divers\Nin the Border Zone immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が… ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（堀）どうするんですか？ 局長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do, Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原）フッ\N（堀）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じきじきの任命\Nありがたく承ります
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will gladly obey your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（グミ）キューキュッ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キュキュ… キュイ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キュイ キュキュイ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グミ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gummi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 どうすれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（グミ）キュイキュイ\N（アイコ）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キュキュキュ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模･楓）くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:18.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の目の前で死なれちゃ\N名折れになるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting someone on my team die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:22.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで俺についてきた？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一樹がアイコを\N助けたいって思うのと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki wants to save Aiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はあんたを死なせたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:44.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントは分かってた\Nアイコは何も悪くないって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew deep down\Nthat Aiko had done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう嫌なんだ\N自分の気持ちにウソつくのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand to lie to myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to find a way\Nto bring us all out of this alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:55.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから私は みんなが\N死ななくてすむ道を探したい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,活性が収まってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Activity has died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは 一樹たちを捜し出す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we find Kazuki and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話は それからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生 先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Yura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N俺は終わるのか？ ここで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this the end for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,篠山(しのやま)さん\N俺を信じてくれたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinoyama, you believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, it's ending here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなのに こんなところで俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）信じていいんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay for me to trust you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（由良）\N僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかで間違ったんだろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}make a mistake somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この先 どこへ進めば…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（由良）\N桐生(きりゅう)先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Kiryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生 僕は まだ\Nあなたに何も返せていない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still haven't paid you back\Nfor what you did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バーストを終息させることさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't even ended the Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:31.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）あっ\N橘アイコ 君は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aiko Tachibana, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやあ～！\N（雄哉）あっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い この人を放して！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let go of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tachibana!\N-No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや！ やめて～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）急ぎましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘アイコ\N君は なぜそんな選択を！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko Tachibana!\NWhy did you choose to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gummi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グミ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キュキュッ キュイ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ あの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さん　亮太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Ryota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さん！ 亮太！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Ryota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, please! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 起きて！ 目を覚まして！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ お母さん 亮太\N起きてったら！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mom! Ryota! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（母）\Nあっ アイコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\Nあ　あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 姉ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（母）\Nアイコ… なのね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\N姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（母）\N大きくなったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ケガは？\N事故のケガは大丈夫なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your injuries?\NAre they all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:23.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　大丈夫 治ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\N姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亮太 大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんが\Nすぐに助けてあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\Nうん　俺 ここから早く出たい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校 行って\N友達とサッカーしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to school and see my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　必ず出してあげる\Nお母さんも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I promise to save you and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（母）\Nあなたは大丈夫なの？\Nここもまた いつ動き出すか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows\Nwhen this will become active again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなただけでも早く逃げなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should escape and save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:08.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橘アイコ）\Nこれは私にしかできないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ　ここは大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:17.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに 一緒にね\N来てくれた人たちもいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some people who came with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\N友達？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何て言えばいいのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what to call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（母）\Nアイコ\Nここまで頑張って来てくれたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko, you've worked so hard to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\Nそういえば 姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Aiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかパワーアップした感じが\Nするもん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem a lot stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ 何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも たくさん笑って泣いたから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've laughed and cried a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が今 こうして\Nここにいられるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole existence here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのおかげなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:57.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が私だから できること
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something that only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\N姉ちゃん どうかした？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong, Aiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううん　何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しだけ こうしてたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to stay here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）ハァ ハァ\Nあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橘！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:24.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉 息切れ）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:40.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎君　私ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:10.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.78,0:24:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by Brian Athey
